Ex-Big Brother Naija housemate, Omashola has publicly declared his love for KimOprah. Omashola made this known on Wednesday episode of BBNaija Reunion hosted by Ebuka Obi-Uchendu. He, however said KimOprah is being difficult with him, but he would not hesitate to put in more efforts. “Kim is not happy with me but I know what I want. “I want KimOprah. I’m ready to do anything for her to be my girlfriend but I feel she’s far away,” Omashola added. When asked if she would accept Omashola as her Boyfriend, Kim said: “Omashola will always be in my corner but his self-centeredness makes it difficult.”